## Example Usage

### Scenario: Approaching Context Limit

```yaml
# Context reaches 80% during implementation
Context Health Check:
  usage: 160000 / 200000 tokens (80%)
  status: warning
  action: checkpoint_created
  checkpoint: ckpt-safety-1769640100
  recommendation: "Consider /compact after current task"

# User continues work, reaches 90%
Context Health Check:
  usage: 180000 / 200000 tokens (90%)
  status: critical
  action: auto_checkpoint
  checkpoint: ckpt-pre-compact-1769640200
  recommendation: "Recommend /compact now to prevent context overflow"

# User runs /compact
Pre-compact Hook:
  1. Load retention rules
  2. Identify critical context (story-042, arch-042, src/auth.ts)
  3. Create checkpoint with critical context
  4. Emit pre-compact event

Native /compact:
  [Claude Code performs compaction]

Post-compact Verification:
  workflow_state: intact
  story_id: story-042 (preserved)
  files_in_progress: ["src/auth.ts"] (preserved)
  tokens_after: 70000
  usage: 35% (healthy)
```
